<section class="border-b border-border pt-16 pb-16 md:pt-24 md:pb-20">
  <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
    <div
      class="bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-zinc-50 uppercase dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-900"
    >
      About Me
    </div>
    <div class="h-px w-12 bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-800"></div>
  </div>

  <h1
    class="mb-12 font-serif text-3xl leading-[1.1] font-medium tracking-tight text-zinc-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-zinc-50"
  >
    写代码，记笔记，<br />
    偶尔<span class="text-muted-foreground italic">发发呆</span>。
  </h1>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-16">
    <div class="md:col-span-8">
      <p
        class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed font-light text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300"
      >
        Hi，我是轻河 👋，一名终身学习的业余全栈开发者。
        <br />
        目前对 Web 和 AI 相关技术领域比较感兴趣，喜欢折腾各种各样的新鲜玩意儿。在这里会记录和分享一些折腾笔记、技术随笔以及碎碎念。
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-bold">
        <a
          href="#blog"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-zinc-900 transition-colors hover:text-indigo-600 dark:text-zinc-100"
        >
          <span class="border-b-2 border-zinc-900 pb-0.5 dark:border-zinc-100"
            >阅读博客</span
          >
          &rarr;
        </a>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="text-zinc-400 transition-colors hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100"
        >
          更多关于我
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:col-span-4">
      <div>
        <span
          class="mb-2 block font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase"
          >Location</span
        >
        <span class="block font-serif text-sm text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200"
          >Xi'an, China</span
        >
      </div>
      <div>
        <span
          class="mb-2 block font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase"
          >Tech</span
        >
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span
            class="border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400"
            >Astro</span
          >
          <span
            class="border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400"
            >TailwindCSS</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
